title: 111_s2071
content: CERTAIN IMAGING COLORANTS. Subchapter II of chapter 99 of the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States is amended by inserting new headings. "9902.01.00 Aryl substituted pyrazonyl sodium salt (PMN No. P03-78) and substituted naphthalene potassium/sodium salt (PMN No. P04-390) provided for in subheading 3215.11.00." "9902.01.00 Copper phthalocyanine substituted with sulphonic acids and alkyl sulphonoamides, sodium/ammonium salts (PMN No. P02-893) provided for in subheading 3215.19.00. On or before 12/31/2011." Sulphonic acids and sulphonoamides, sodium salts (CAS No. 90295-11-7) provided for in subheading 3215.19.00. Copper phthalocyanine substituted with sulphonic acids and alkyl sulphonoamides, sodium salt (CAS No.) provided for in subheading 3215.19.00. Substituted naphthalenylazol alkoxyl phenyl azo carboxyphenylene. Substituted naphthalenylazol alkoxyl phenyl azo carboxyphenylene and copper phthalocyanine substituted with sulphonic acids and sulphonoamides, sodium salts are provided for in subheading 3215.19.00. Substituted naphthalenylazol alkoxyl phenyl azo carboxyphenylene and copper phthalocyanine substituted with sulphonic acids and sulphonoamides, sodium salts are provided for in subheading 3215.19.00. Aminoalkyl triazinediylbis substituted phenylene azo bis, sodium salt (CAS No. 50925-42-3) and chloro substituted naphthalenylazo substituted naphthalenyl azo carboxyphenylene, sodium salt (PMN No. P-90-394) fall under tariff heading 9902.01.00. Subheading 3215.11.00 includes Aryl [Substituted phenylazo] pyridine, sodium/lithium salt (PMN No. P-02-234) and Amino] triazinyl] amino] benzoic acid, sodium/lithium salts (PMN No. P-83-386) under tariff heading 9902.01.00. No changes are made, and the products should be provided on or before 12/31/2011. The effective date for the amendment made by subsection (a) is the 15th day after the enactment of this Act.
